title: Ciena 5171: PM instance Tx/Rx Bytes
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/ciena
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors

 - the bytes transmitted per second

 - the bytes received per second

 The check always returns {OK}.

 This check supports the Ciena 5171 Packetwave Platform.

 The relevant MIB is CIENA-CES-PM.

item:
 The instance name as provided by the device.

discovery:
 One service is created for each instance reporting measurements.
